{
  "stem": "1061.1",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I am the youngest of the three.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "My mother's name was Poline or Pola.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Her maiden name Tenenblum.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "She came from central Poland, [INAUDIBLE] and [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "My father was-- his name was Isaac Laks.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And he came from [INAUDIBLE], which is Western Poland.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And the difference in their backgrounds was that my father was really educated in the German language.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Even though he was a Polish citizen, his basic and higher education was in German.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So my father spoke German fluently.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And he had his encyclopedia in German and his-- his literature was German.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "But his Polish, of course, was beautiful.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Mother's on the other hand, was-- had a mixture of the Russian, because as everyone knows from history, Poland was, prior to the First War, divided into three units, Russian, German, and Austrian.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "My mother came from the so-called Russian part.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Anyhow, my father, as I said, came from [INAUDIBLE] in the western part, mother from central Poland from a very large family.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And mother's-- my grandmother, Tenenblum, had 13 children.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "She bore 13 children, nine of whom survived.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And these, of course, like my mother, had their own families.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "So that gives you an idea how large my mother's family was.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And of course, all of them perished.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And well, we lived a very good life.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "We had a very, very kind of a comfortable life.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "My parents-- my mother was very much involved in the Zionist movement.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "She was president of the Women's International Zionist Organization, WIZO, for the district, whether it was the-- I don't know how large the district was, but it probably encompassed number of towns.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "My father was an engineer in the forestry lumber industry.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And both were very well educated.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And the three of us, my oldest sister is Anna, presently Wilson.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
